title: LF Team Plat 3 Mid main
body:
Hello guys,

I am climbing through season 8 steadily and want to get out there and see if theres any teams that need subs or teams I could train with for future prospects. I am a Mid main this season and main zed, zoe and taliyah. I can also play alot of the other mid laners and willing to learn picks that would benefit team play. I feel I can bring alot, not so much in shot calling but rather I have the raw skill, I just need people to help mould me into a better player. 

IGN is fat australiàn

Hmu with anything thanks
